{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "broker-charts-api-collection",
    "name": "Broker Service — Charts & Market Data",
    "description": "API collection for testing the Broker Service intraday and historical data endpoints.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Set the `baseUrl` variable to your server URL (default: `http://localhost:3000`)\n2. Ensure the server is running (`pnpm dev`)\n3. Ensure a broker adapter is active (Dhan or Mock)\n\n**Endpoints:**\n- POST /api/broker/charts/intraday — Intraday OHLCV candles (1/5/15/25/60 min)\n- POST /api/broker/charts/historical — Daily historical OHLCV candles\n- GET /api/broker/status — Broker service status\n- GET /api/broker/token/status — Token validity check",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Status & Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Broker Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/broker/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "broker", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Check the overall broker service status — active adapter, connection state, kill switch status."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Token Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/broker/token/status",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "broker", "token", "status"]
            },
            "description": "Check if the current broker access token is valid."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Charts — Intraday",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Intraday — NIFTY 50 Index (5 min)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"securityId\": \"13\",\n  \"exchangeSegment\": \"IDX_I\",\n  \"instrument\": \"INDEX\",\n  \"interval\": \"5\",\n  \"fromDate\": \"2026-04-04 09:15:00\",\n  \"toDate\": \"2026-04-04 15:30:00\",\n  \"oi\": false\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/broker/charts/intraday",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "broker", "charts", "intraday"]
            },
            "description": "Get 5-minute intraday candles for NIFTY 50 index.\n\n**Parameters:**\n- `securityId`: \"13\" (NIFTY 50 on Dhan)\n- `exchangeSegment`: \"IDX_I\" (Index segment)\n- `instrument`: \"INDEX\"\n- `interval`: \"5\" (5-minute candles)\n- `fromDate` / `toDate`: Date range in \"YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss\" format\n- `oi`: false (no open interest for index)"
          },
          "response": []
        },
